title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
